Package: commentr2md
Type: Package
Title: Extracts the comments from a file that uses the #' commenting standard, and converts the content of the file into a markdown and html file
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alex Lopes
Maintainer: Alex Lopes <alxcrv@gmail.com>
Description: 
    The package is composed of two functions, get_comments() and make_md(), and they are used in conjunction.
    The user will simply execute make_md(path_to_file), and the script will create a .md and .html file in the working directory.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports: markdown, utils
